race.description: Greyhounds As Pets Mixed Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: RICKI'S BURNER (2) comes here after a sizzling Grade 5 win at this track over 395m in 22.14. Has the ability and looks hard to top. LOCHINVAR TIGER (7) is better than last start when sixth (23.98) from Box 6 at Horsham over 410m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Cannot be left out. TERRIFIC IZZY (4) goes very well this course and distance starting 14 times for five wins and seven minors. Was out of the placings last time (20.59) at Angle Park in a Grade 4/5, finishing sixth and beaten 11 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances.  Something for the Multiples: WIRRULLA HARRY (1)
